powerpc/32: replace LOAD_MSR_KERNEL() by LOAD_REG_IMMEDIATE()

LOAD_MSR_KERNEL() and LOAD_REG_IMMEDIATE() are doing the same thing
in the same way. Drop LOAD_MSR_KERNEL()

